        "<p>In doing some work on a project I stumbled across a formatting situation on a couple of websites that I couldn't explain.<\/p>\n\n<p>When viewing the markup in the Google Chrome DOM inspector, some values appear with quotes around them. These quotes do not appear in either the HTML source nor the rendered page.<\/p>\n\n<p>The format is as follows:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;span class=\"...\"&gt;$&lt;\/span&gt;\n\"XX.\"\n&lt;span class=\"...\"&gt;xx&lt;\/span&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>OR<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>\"$XX.\"\n&lt;span",
